sources.title: Pancho Villa (1972 Western) Telly Savalas - The only man to invade the U.S.A.! en español
sources.description:
A double-cross in an arms deal prompts Mexican revolutionary Pancho Villa to launch a daring raid on a U.S. Army weapons depot in Columbus, New Mexico. The conflict escalates into a high-stakes train collision and explosive battles as Villa fights to advance his revolution and evade capture.

Director: Eugenio Martín
Writers: Eugenio Martín, Julian Zimet
Genres: Action, Biography, Comedy, Drama, Western

Main actors: 
Telly Savalas - Pancho Villa
Clint Walker - Scotty
Chuck Connors - Col. Wilcox
Anne Francis - Flo
José María Prada - Luis
Ángel del Pozo - Lt. Eager
Luis Dávila - McDermott
Mónica Randall - Lupe
Antonio Casas - General Goyo
Alberto Dalbés - Captain Mendoza
Walter Coy - General Pershing
